lead_paragraph: Germany's Nico Rosberg celebrated his first Formula One world championship on Sunday after finishing runner-up in a tense Abu Dhabi Grand Prix won by Mercedes team mate Lewis Hamilton amid accusations of 'dirty tricks'.

headline.print_headline: Rosberg Takes Formula One Title From Hamilton
headline.main: Rosberg Takes Formula One Title From Hamilton
